name: Satoshi's Cyphers 08
description: The Key text to solve all 12 of these cyphers will be available on the mainpage of satoshiscrypt.com at 11:59 PM PST 4/18/2021. The first to solve each of these cyphers will receive an Archetype Tarot 1 of 1 NFT Trophy on Tezos from Salvador Satoshi. Best of luck to you all.
